creator: We Soft
descriptionHtml:
Media Player HD have both audio media player and video player. This All in one application is very useful as its offers multiple functionalities in one app.

Media Player HD Feature of this app play all video and audio files form you Android Phone .Media Player For Android is the Media Player which Support almost all media files such as: RMVB,MKV,AVI,MP4,WMV,FLMPEG ,RM , ASF .The Media Player is a free and open source cross-platform media player that plays most media files. The player has a media library for especially for video files , and allows to browse folders directly .Media Player For Android Support control volume and brightness and also includes a widget for video control. Media Player HD also supports headsets control.
Features of Media Player 2021
1) Support Both Audio and Video Tracks.so the app is a video player Hd and Audio player at the same time :
- 2) The feature is media player for all formats which Support almost all Video formats :AVI,MP4,WMV,FLV,MPEG ,RM , RMVB ,ASF,MKV , MOV , OGX
3) Create your own playlists using this app to listen music .

For any complaints and Feature requests about this app please contact us at :
wesoft60@gmail.com
